dct_title_s: Provincia Oxoniensis: Oxfordshire; Amstelodami, Apud Ioannem Ianssonium.; Province of Oxford
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Includes illustrations of cherubims around the scale cartouche. Does not match any state listed in Van der Krogt. From the Jansson Appendix Atlas 1636-1680, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map; 37 x 47 cm.
